headline: Stanley Black & Decker To Present At The 2025 Goldman Sachs Industrials And Materials Conference
summary: Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK) invites investors and the general public to listen to a webcast of a presentation by Pat Hallinan, Executive Vice President and CFO, at the 2025 Goldman Sachs Industrials and Materials Conference on Thursday, December 4, 2025 at 11:30 AM ET.
